headline.print_headline: Moyes Can Smile at Last as United Sink Swansea
headline.main: Moyes Can Smile at Last as United Sink Swansea

lead_paragraph: Manchester United returned to winning ways after three straight defeats with a 2-0 Premier League home victory over Swansea City on Saturday, avenging last week's FA Cup loss to the Welsh club.
